{"tid":582572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【IT狗翻身】會計師睇經濟 4年來最樂觀！IT潛力最大","createTime":"2018-03-06T09:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:31:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06233414ea86e42c4522b467bf1f6197556a203c","tid":582572,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:53:00.000Z","msg":"ACCA（特許公認會計師公會）香港分會調查顯示，受訪會計財務人員對香港2018的經濟表現較去年顯著樂觀，當中認為經濟表現好/非常好的由上年的5%大幅增長至32%，而預料經濟表現為差/非常差的則由去年的37%大幅至8%，反映受訪者對經濟前景信心回升。<br />\n<br />\n至於行業發展方面，最具增長潛力的行業依次為<span style=\"color: red;\">「資訊科技及電訊」</span>、「醫療保健」及「金融、銀行及保險」。不過「零售」因網購盛行以及租金高企等因素，將於2018年面對最大的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515643842_5102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515643842_5102.jpg&h=c2f76444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180111/57693289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F57693289&d=AiK%2FvUy3SAFDSmMwJ3%2B860%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=856d133e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F57693289&h=4ddcd562\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180111/57693289</a>"},{"pid":"82eb5a093723e51111cf2c263a91777cbd6398b0","tid":582572,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"老貓去返工啦"},{"pid":"d077cca132345d27643a239101be0aff0c825643","tid":582572,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:02:51.000Z","msg":"股災來了重講呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b62826c0c7fecf2ff93c89a73539582c093d1b","tid":582572,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply